 10 INPUT "What is the X for the desired point?"; X -the user inputs their desired X
 20 INPUT "What is the Y for the desired point?"; Y -the user inputs their desired Y
 39 CLS -Clears Screen
 30 LOCATE X, Y -Program locates the users inputted X and Y
 40 PRINT CHR$(219) -Prints a live cell on the users designated point

